# ═══ Default-DENY gitignore for the public showroom ═══
# Everything is ignored unless explicitly allowed below. A stray file dragged
# into this folder can NOT be committed by accident — it must be whitelisted here.

# 1) deny everything
*

# 2) allow the repo's own files
!.gitignore
!README.md
!DISCLAIMER.md
!PUBLISH.md

# 3) allow the six content folders (dir must be un-ignored before its contents)
!reports/
!reports/**
!charts/
!charts/**
!essays/
!essays/**
!methodology/
!methodology/**
!track-record/
!track-record/**
!template/
!template/**

# 4) re-deny dangerous shapes even inside allowed folders (belt and braces)
**/*_internal.*
**/*.py
**/SKILL.md
**/.env*
**/*.key
**/*apikey*
**/*secret*
**/*credentials*
